channel.title: Starting mopar error
channel.description:
I know this may seem rather noobish but this computer acts very weird relating to moparscape. I have ran moparscape and working on my own server on my other comp. But this comp is very weird. Most of the time when i try to run mopat it says that another program is using this file. Last night it worked. Today it didnt and just a second ago i rebooted and this is the error when i try to run mopar...
